{
  "stem": "9987.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I'm already a legal person, in case I get stopped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a legal passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That lasted until approximately March, 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, March 1943-- OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The bridge was finally finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, their company was going back to-- to western Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's no way I could go with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was no way that Dukhowski would take me with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a conversation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says-- they used to call me Jasiu-- Jan, short in-- in Polish is Jasiu.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, Jasiu, I did what I could for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The company is finished here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're leaving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can't go with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, from now on, you are on your own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only favor I have to ask you, if you ever get caught, remember I never knew who you were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't put me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Arbeitsamt, which is the-- the-- the office of-- Of the workers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the workers-- providing workers, came an order that all Poles that got out of the jobs in here, had to come to register to go to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these local Poles did not want to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they decided that they're going to run away into the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was all forest lands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since I'm a Pole, and I don't want to go to Germany either, so I run away to the forest together with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whether they liked it or not, we became part of the group, a resistance group--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a Polish resistance group of approximately 100 Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Catholic poles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now the Poles had hidden arms from before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were their homes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they dug out their arms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everyone got a gun or a rifle, not too much ammunition.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
